 * Mixing ARB and NV vertex/fragment programs can be tricky.
 * Note: GL_VERTEX_PROGRAM_ARB == GL_VERTEX_PROGRAM_NV
 *  but, GL_FRAGMENT_PROGRAM_ARB != GL_FRAGMENT_PROGRAM_NV
